{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":542756,"duration_api_ms":397503,"num_turns":47,"result":"All done. Here's a summary of what was fixed:\n\n## Phase 1 PartnerContacts — Complete\n\n### Fix 1: i18n Keys Showing as Raw Text (BUG-PC-016, P0)\n**Problem:** All text showed raw i18n keys like `partnercontacts.page_title` instead of readable text.\n**Root cause:** Base44's `t()` function returns the key itself when no translation exists, ignoring the second argument.\n**Fix:** Shadowed `t` with a fallback-aware wrapper (same proven pattern from CartView.jsx):\n```js\nconst { t: _t } = useI18n();\nconst t = (key, fallback) => {\n  const val = typeof _t === \"function\" ? _t(key) : \"\";\n  if (!val || typeof val !== \"string\") return fallback;\n  const norm = val.trim();\n  if (norm === key || norm.startsWith(key + \":\")) return fallback;\n  return norm;\n};\n```\nThis required only **2 edits** (main component + error boundary wrapper) — all 50+ existing `t('key', 'fallback')` calls automatically work with no downstream changes.\n\n### Fix 2: Touch Targets (BUG-PC-017–020, P2)\n- **Icon buttons** (edit/toggle/delete): `min-h-[44px] min-w-[44px]`\n- **View mode toggles**: `min-h-[44px]`\n- **Checkbox**: `w-5 h-5` + `cursor-pointer` on label\n- **Button gap**: `gap-1` → `gap-2` (8px spacing)\n\n### Deliverables\n- `partnercontacts1_v1.2_RELEASE.jsx` — ready for Base44\n- `BUGS.md` — 12 fixed, 9 active (P2-P3)\n- `README.md` — page description + RELEASE history + UX changelog\n- Git pushed: `a2e9277`","stop_reason":null,"session_id":"588b79d8-57d4-4cd2-b90e-8a9e60541414","total_cost_usd":2.0720620000000003,"usage":{"input_tokens":100,"cache_creation_input_tokens":118722,"cache_read_input_tokens":1622499,"output_tokens":20423,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":118722,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":